    "url": "docs/doc2-muvico-secured-2029.html#sec-13-03",
    "summary": "Communication by Holders with Other Holders. Holders may communicate with each other about their rights under TIA Section 312(b). The Company, Trustee, and Registrar have the protection of TIA Section 312(c). Why it matters: This facilitates...",
    "keywords": "",
    "content": "Communication by Holders with Other Holders. Holders may communicate with each other about their rights under TIA Section 312(b). The Company, Trustee, and Registrar have the protection of TIA Section 312(c). Why it matters: This facilitates collective action by holders, which is essential in contested restructurings where holders need to organize and coordinate. Holders may communicate pursuant to TIA Section 312(b) with other Holders with respect to their rights under this Indenture or the Notes. The Company, the Trustee, the Registrar and anyone else shall have the protection of TIA Section 312(c)."
