    "content": "Successors. Governs mergers, consolidations, and sales of all or substantially all assets. The surviving entity must assume all obligations under the indenture, be organized in the US, and not cause a Default. Why it matters: Prevents Muvico from restructuring itself out from under these note obligations through a corporate reorganization while preserving continuity of the lien structure."
