    "keywords": "",
    "content": "Excluded lenders challenged the double-dip structure aggressively. Key arguments: impermissible subordination; intercompany loan mechanism was a fraudulent device; asset transfers violated restrictive covenants. The case created novel legal questions not fully addressed by Serta precedent."
