    "summary": "A lender can score a credit agreement’s LME vulnerability on a 0-100 scale: Category Weight Scoring Criteria Anti-Priming 30% 0 = no protection; 50 = partial; 100 = comprehensive Anti-Dropdown 20% 0 = no J.Crew blocker; 50 = partial; 100 =...",
