    "url": "research/countermeasures.html#art-summary",
    "summary": "This document covers all eight requested areas: Anti-Serta / Anti-Uptier Provisions – Full mechanics of uptier attacks, detailed sample drafting language at multiple sophistication levels, the “affected lender” consent framework, five known...",
    "keywords": "",
    "content": "This document covers all eight requested areas: Anti-Serta / Anti-Uptier Provisions – Full mechanics of uptier attacks, detailed sample drafting language at multiple sophistication levels, the “affected lender” consent framework, five known workarounds with counter-defenses, and adoption rates from 2020-2025. J.Crew Blockers / Anti-Dropdown Provisions – Asset dropdown mechanics, four categories of defensive provisions (designation restrictions, transfer restrictions, investment caps, and the stronger 2024+ formulations), five workarounds, and adoption trajectory. Anti-Double-Dip Provisions – Structural double-dip mechanics with Envision/Robertshaw/Incora examples, three categories of defensive drafting (intercompany loan restrictions, comprehensive no-double-dip covenant, intercompany subordination), four workarounds, and adoption data. Cooperation Agreement Templates – Complete template covering minimum participation thresholds, proposed transaction definitions, side deal restrictions with MFN, fiduciary out (including CLO-specific considerations), information sharing/MNPI protocols, and term/termination provisions, plus a generational comparison table. Sacred Rights Evolution – Full comparative framework of traditional vs. expanded sacred rights, complete sample expanded sacred rights provision (16 categories), yank-a-bank interaction fix, and adoption matrix. Pro-Rata Sharing and Waterfall Protections – Anti-non-pro-rata exchange provisions, MFN for exchanges, anti-non-pro-rata prepayment provisions, and four workarounds. Restricted Payments and Investment Basket Tightening – Available Amount basket comparison (traditional vs. tightened), builder basket restrictions, anti-stacking provisions, restricted investment categories, and the multi-layer governance framework. Market Trends 2024-2026 – Four-tier adoption framework, BSL vs. direct lending comparison, rating agency and CLO manager responses, regulatory developments, and the complete documentation arms race timeline. The document also includes a Lender’s Evaluation Checklist with a scoring framework applicable to the AMC case competition, plus appendices covering case law precedents, model provision quick reference, and a full glossary."
